    "Consider the entire task jointly.",
    "If we can obtain image captioning datasets containing the celebrities' name, we can customize certain loss and improve the model's ability to recognize faces.",
    "Joint model may have better grammatical accuracy then our separate-steps pipeline.",
    "[18,46] ConclusionIn this paper, we use a combined pipeline to conduct image captioning for celebrities.",
